							ExportMethod {abstract}	
								or
									SentViaEmail
									DirectDownload
							Format {abstract}	
								optional
									CSV
									XLSX
							Frequency {abstract}	
								optional
									OneTime
									Periodically
			UserManagement {abstract}	
				mandatory
					AddUser

				optional
					ChooseRole
					DeleteUser
